languages.text: "С него не убудет. Раз уж на то пошло — пускай его самого в питании урежут, а то штаны у Высокого фактотума год от года все шире становятся".
"I think he's got a few scraps to spare. Come to think of it, it's about time someone cut HIS rations — the High Factotum's trousers go up a size every year."

languages.text: « Il a bien quelques miettes à partager. Maintenant que j'y pense, il serait grand temps que quelqu'un limite les rations du haut factotum... Ses pantalons prennent une taille par an. »
languages.original_text: "I think he's got a few scraps to spare. Come to think of it, it's about time someone cut HIS rations — the High Factotum's trousers go up a size every year."

languages.text: “我猜他应该还有点瓶瓶罐罐可以分出来吧。想想看，也确实有人该克扣一下他的口粮了，咱们的高阶顾问肚子真是越来越圆了。”
languages.original_text: "I think he's got a few scraps to spare. Come to think of it, it's about time someone cut HIS rations — the High Factotum's trousers go up a size every year."

languages.text: "Ich denke, er kann durchaus etwas abgeben. Abgesehen davon wird es Zeit, SEINE Rationen mal zu kürzen – das Hoch-Faktotum braucht jedes Jahr größere Hosen."
languages.original_text: "I think he's got a few scraps to spare. Come to think of it, it's about time someone cut HIS rations — the High Factotum's trousers go up a size every year."

languages.text: «Creo que tiene algunos restos para compartir. Y ahora que lo pienso, deberían reducir sus raciones; el Sumo Factótum necesita una talla más de pantalón cada año».

languages.text: "Vardır kenarda köşede bir şeyleri. Bir düşündüm de KENDİ erzaklarından da verebilir gayet. Arşıkâhya'nın cepleri her sene daha da doluyor."
